Package fr.insa.IA.IA

Class InfoSet

java.lang.Object
fr.insa.IA.IA.InfoSet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class InfoSet extends Object implements Serializable
InfoSet for our simplified Belote. An infoset contains all the known information at a point in the game : already played cards, cards in hand, opponent card in his table, ...
Author:
AUGEREAU Jeremy, GRAC Guilhem
